	(text "Cat Feeder power architecture:\n18650 -> TP4056 (charge/protect) -> OUT+ splits:\n  (a) directly to ESP32-C3 5V/VIN pin (LDO makes 3.3V)\n  (b) to AP3602A boost VIN -> VOUT 5V -> ULN2003 V+ and motor\nESP32 GPIO10 controls boost EN (off during deep sleep).\n1000uF buffers motor start brown-out. 100nF decouples ESP32.\nCOM of stepper -> 5V enables ULN2003 flyback diodes.\nButton GPIO9 -> GND (INPUT_PULLUP, wake source)."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 25.4 30.48 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.5 1.5)
			)
			(justify left top)
		)
		(uuid "47bd304e-254f-465f-adc7-c3b7222c71d0")
	)
